data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!!!! Up to $5,000.00 towards closing cost with acceptable offer!!!Step into the future of stylish home living in this stunning two-story residence, featuring 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. Nestled in the sought-after Northwoods Estate community, this masterpiece offers seamless access to Charleston's vibrant heart, the airport, air force base, Boeing, outlets, and I-26.Indulge in the epitome of elegance with granite countertops and floors throughout, elevating the aesthetic of every room. Say goodbye to HOA fees as you settle into this spacious haven, gracefully positioned on a 0.24-acre lot within a tranquil cul-de-sac. Your dream home awaits, presenting the perfect canvas for your next chapter. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity--seize it today!
